Package: siscreenr
Type: Package
Date: 2019-04-08
Title: Analysis of siRNA-based High Content Screening
Author: person('Aleksander', 'Chlebowski', email = 'olobiolo@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Maintainer: <olobiolo@gmail.com>
Version: 2.6.3
Description: Set of functions I use to analyze high throughput microscopy data.
    They cover data loading, normalization, scoring, annotation and reporting.
    Some plotting wrappers are also inclued.
    The package is adjusted to particular result file formats and my usual work routine. It may not work for everyone.
